p to it."],[2631,2740,"Yeah, Mr. Trenton!"],[2773,2948,"We were following Allison’s lead!"],[2948,3082,"It's all her fault!"],[3148,3282,"Call the university president."],[3319,3449,"I want them expelled."],[3461,3653,"And I will be pressing charges."],[3687,3899,"Mr. Trenton, my father is"],[3899,4095,"Richard Kane from the Kane group."],[4145,4254,"I mean, you can see this, like,"],[4254,4358,"one little oversight."],[4358,4471,"And just forgive me."],[4508,4604,"Thank you for reminding me,"],[4604,4713,"Allison."],[4713,4808,"Cancel our contract"],[4808,4942,"with Kane Enterprises."],[5184,5284,"Bankrupt them."],[5380,5451,"No, no... Yes, sir."],[5451,5559,"No, no, no, no!"],[5559,5643,"Daddy!"],[6006,6114,"Everything will be fine,"],[6114,6172,"Harper."],[6197,6377,"I'm taking you to the hospital right now."],[6377,6506,"Please save our baby."]],"18":[[821,988,"I'm so sorry, Mr. Trenton."],[1042,1176,"Miss Jenkins is fine but,"],[1263,1372,"she lost the baby."],[4225,4320,"How’s the baby?"],[4575,4633,"Um..."],[4733,4888,"God, I’m so sorry, Harper."],[4967,5055,"I'm so sorry."],[5376,5534,"No, no!"],[5534,5684,"Not my.... Not my baby!"],[5789,5868,"Oh my God!"],[6064,6218,"This is all my fault."]],"19":[[50,200,"I should've been more careful."],[283,387,"I should've known that they"],[387,567,"would come for me and my baby."],[650,855,"It's not your fault. It's not your fault."],[900,1101,"Shhhh."],[1276,1363,"There's no way that you could"],[1363,1447,"have foreseen that."],[1447,1514,"Okay?"],[1843,1960,"You need to get some rest."],[2168,2306,"Your top priority right now"],[2314,2402,"is to get better."],[3566,3728,"I'd do anything just to stop her"],[3728,3795,"from crying."],[3899,4004,"Should I feel this way?"],[4095,4250,"Is this feeling for the baby,"],[4316,4408,"or for her?"]],"20":[[350,442,"Uh, Will..."],[583,784,"I think it's time that I move out."],[813,892,"It's..."],[963,1084,"It's been weeks."],[1626,1751,"No, please."],[1835,1989,"Harper, you can stay as long as you want."],[1989,2185,"I mean, the car is a gift."],[2419,2502,"It's the least I can do."],[2502,2631,"After everything I put you through."],[2731,2815,"Thank you."],[2877,3036,"I'm recovered now."],[3169,3407,"I don't want to bother you any longer."],[3470,3586,"I'm going to move out..."],[3645,3741,"tomorrow."],[4291,4425,"I want you to stay."],[4491,4804,"But... there's no reason for you to."]],"21":[[417,446,"Will?"],[738,784,"Sorry."],[784,875,"Did I wake you?"],[900,980,"No, I..."],[1071,1188,"I couldn't sleep either."],[2143,2348,"I'm really sorry about the baby,"],[2369,2427,"Will."],[2452,2556,"I thought that I was doing"],[2556,2761,"this whole surrogacy thing for my family."],[2761,2965,"Because, you know, we needed an heir."],[3069,3194,"But when the doctor told me"],[3194,3315,"that we lost the baby,"],[3349,3553,"I felt something missing."],[3645,3903,"And in these moments today,"],[3903,4041,"I've had the realization"],[4041,4283,"that I want to be a father."],[4416,4542,"I'm ready to be a dad."],[4662,4804,"Then let's try again."],[4884,4963,"No, Harper."],[4963,5084,"No. I can not put you through"],[5084,5130,"that again."],[5130,5251,"I'll find another way."],[5251,5417,"No, no. Will, I..."],[5622,5943,"I want to have this baby with you."]],"22":[[266,421,"Are you sure about that?"],[629,704,"Yes."],[1292,1651,"But, no more surgeries. I..."],[1797,1926,"I can't have those terrifying"],[1926,2143,"needles inside of me ever again."],[2198,2427,"Okay. No more needles."],[2602,2673,"I can"],[2790,3090,"put something less terrifying"],[3153,3249,"inside of you."],[3436,3553,"But I cannot promise you"],[3553,3703,"that it won't be thrilling."]],"23":[[767,784,"Wait."],[784,921,"No, no, no, wait. Hold on."],[921,1009,"What am I doing?"],[1101,1222,"Harper, you're still a virgin."],[1222,1347,"I can't take advantage of you"],[1347,1434,"like this."],[1434,1651,"I'm not a girl who treasures"],[1651,1801,"her virginity."],[1851,2223,"I know, you want me too."],[2252,2419,"I didn't pay for your virginity, Harper."],[2419,2598,"It's not in the contract. Okay?"],[2702,2819,"You would regret this moment"],[2819,2915,"that it happened."],[2915,3036,"No, I won't."],[3636,3716,"Will, I..."],[3753,3874,"I want you,"],[3937,3999,"Will."],[5822,5955,"I'll go slow,"],[6072,6197,"and you just tell me,"],[6331,6431,"exactly"],[6531,6635,"how you want it."]],"24":[[2018,2110,"I'm right here."],[2231,2352,"Just breathe, okay?"],[2352,2506,"I got you. -Okay."],[3053,3157,"How was class today?"],[3286,3465,"You barely got any sleep last night."],[3853,4004,"Somebody stop him!"],[4016,4208,"He just snatched my purse!"],[5372,5484,"Not again!"],[6493,6660,"Oh! Ah! Fuck!"],[7311,7369,"Are you okay?"],[7369,7469,"I'm okay."],[7486,7561,"Thank you."]],"25":[[91,171,"Are you okay?"],[171,241,"Yeah."],[241,321,"Watch out!"],[1159,1234,"Did he hurt you?"],[1259,1334,"No."],[1451,1518,"I'm okay."],[1518,1580,"Thank you."],[1943,2173,"Oh, thank you both so much."],[2173,2373,"You make a wonderful couple."],[2414,2623,"Oh, we're not a couple."],[2623,2698,"Awww."],[2698,2823,"But I would like to get to know"],[2823,2886,"you more."],[2961,3073,"Can I ask if you'd like to join me"],[3073,3157,"for coffee?"],[3228,3336,"You can pepper spray me after"],[3336,3465,"if you're not interested."],[4033,4279,"Thank you for the offer, but I'm busy."],[4325,4400,"Excuse me."],[4446,4521,"I gotta go."],[4612,4683,"Hey, wait!"],[4700,4767,"What’s your..."],[4767,4900,"You got to get that out"],[4900,5109,"faster next time, boy."],[5138,5242,"And you know,"],[5242,5534,"here's a bit of advice from an older lady."],[5584,5951,"If you like the girl, you gotta go for it."],[5993,6114,"There was something there"],[6114,6197,"between you."],[7086,7211,"Harper Jenkins."]],"26":[[529,600,"Come in."],[1121,1184,"Harper."],[1217,1322,"What are you doing here?"],[1518,1651,"I wasn't expecting you to come by."],[2460,2544,"I missed you."],[3186,3411,"And I'm ovulating."],[3620,3695,"And I thought"],[3695,3933,"maybe you could fix that."],[4020,4154,"Well, tell me how you'd like me"],[4154,4320,"to fix that for you."],[4396,4696,"I want you to take me quietly right here,"],[4792,4875,"right now."],[5034,5096,"I don't know."],[5226,5417,"I'm not one for quiet pleasantries."]],"27":[[1009,1184,"Sir, is everything okay?"],[1251,1388,"Walk away, Frank!"],[1397,1484,"We're busy."],[1685,1751,"Will."],[1847,1926,"You want me to let him in?"],[1926,2052,"Or would you rather I continue?"],[2068,2168,"Oh!"],[2419,2548,"Okay."],[3311,3374,"Will."],[3691,3762,"I'm surprised"],[3762,3866,"no other man has thrown"],[3866,3953,"themselves at you."],[4366,4446,"It's not that."],[4446,4508,"It's just..."],[4629,4696,"I'm picky."],[5789,6064,"Wait. I've never done that before."],[6231,6289,"Don't worry."],[6431,6506,"You'll love it."]],"28":[[1355,1518,"I know he probably only had sex"],[1518,1655,"with me to make a baby."],[1685,1901,"That's what our contract says,"],[1901,1993,"after all."],[2957,3178,"But the way he kisses"],[3178,3294,"and touches me,"],[3328,3591,"it felt like we were making love."],[3624,3820,"Am I overthinking this?"],[4037,4179,"Where are my panties?"],[4396,4508,"I'll let you know if anything"],[4508,4571,"comes up."],[4700,4838,"Will, have you seen my panties?"]],"29":[[196,296,"So sorry."],[296,396,"Excuse me."],[467,538,"Please continue."],[880,992,"We'll discuss this tomorrow."],[2210,2273,"Harper!"],[4070,4279,"Is Kaitlin, Will's ex?"],[4441,4504,"Coming in."],[4721,4913,"Sorry, I didn't mean to."],[5138,5259,"Is Kaitlin"],[5259,5372,"your ex?"]],"30":[[913,1038,"It's just something from my past."],[1213,1292,"Come on."],[1488,1576,"Let's get out of here."],[1976,2206,"Kaitlin must be important to Will."],[2206,2389,"But why do I care?"],[2389,2615,"It's not like we're dating or anything."],[3278,3390,"Hey, miss!"],[3390,3486,"I still have your..."],[3712,3770,"Book."],[3870,4049,"Mr. Trenton’s waiting for you in his office."],[4145,4233,"Do you know the woman"],[4233,4329,"who just got into the elevator?"],[4408,4508,"Probably an intern."],[4508,4650,"So she works for my big brother."]],"31":[[241,429,"Oh, hey, big bro."],[429,633,"So, changed my mind."],[633,767,"I want to work here, uh..."],[767,959,"So, find me a desk."],[1001,1109,"Didn't you say that you would"],[1109,1284,"rather have grandpa sell all your"],[1284,1380,"motorcycles"],[1426,1518,"than to go down the corporate"],[1518,1601,"highway to hell?"],[1780,1851,"I met someone."],[1989,2131,"I think she might be the one."],[2406,2469,"Really?"],[2531,2673,"The young Mr. Aaron Trenton"],[2673,2773,"is interested in someone?"],[2915,3136,"Well, that's very uncharacteristic"],[3136,3194,"of you."],[3228,3311,"I don't really see what that has"],[3311,3399,"to do with my company."],[3420,3528,"She works here."],[3803,3920,"When did you become the hopeless"],[3920,4054,"romantic type, man?"],[4233,4379,"Look Aaron. I love you, okay?"],[4379,4487,"I'm happy for you."],[4529,4654,"But if you're going to work for me,"],[4675,4808,"you need to actually do work."],[4854,4917,"Yes, sir."],[4988,5067,"You're the boss."],[5588,5697,"Is that Kaitlin?"],[5822,5922,"You kept her photo after"],[5922,6035,"all she did to you?"],[6189,6352,"Looks like you're still not over her, bro."],[6398,6548,"It's in the trash can for a reason."],[6619,6702,"Besides, it was"],[6735,6877,"forgotten in my closet."],[6919,7057,"Frankly, it's none of your business."],[7057,7111,"Now,"],[7148,7240,"I have work to do."],[7286,7323,"Yeah."],[7323,7424,"Yeah, I'm gone."],[7436,7486,"See ya."]],"32":[[542,592,"Hello?"],[613,771,"Hey, Ms. Jenkins."],[771,980,"Sorry for calling out of the blue like this."],[980,1101,"It's Aaron."],[1101,1213,"We met the other day when"],[1213,1343,"that guy attacked you."],[1380,1509,"Oh, yeah, yeah."],[1509,1680,"How... How did you get my number?"],[1680,1981,"Oh, sorry you left your book."],[2097,2206,"It had your name in it."],[2206,2293,"I asked around campus"],[2293,2377,"for your number."],[2377,2623,"Sorry. Maybe that was overstepping."],[2623,2777,"Uh, I... I felt bad because I had"],[2777,2869,"your property and..."],[2919,2977,"Ugh."],[3007,3140,"Anyway, uh..."],[3161,3336,"what I wanted to ask was, uh..."],[3336,3436,"would you be interested in"],[3436,3607,"joining me for coffee tomorrow?"],[3607,3745,"I can give you your book back."],[3745,3941,"Is he asking me out?"]],"33":[[141,196,"I'm sorry."],[196,442,"I've... I've been really busy lately."],[475,571,"You know, don't even"],[571,667,"worry about it."],[667,771,"I won’t be back to school"],[771,859,"until graduation."],[1101,1205,"Uh, bye!"],[1288,1359,"Who was that?"],[1539,1589,"No one."],[1589,1810,"Uh, I was just checking my email"],[1810,1976,"about the graduation ceremony."],[2089,2231,"Can't believe it's been four years."],[2231,2427,"I'm graduating."],[2427,2527,"Well, actually,"],[2656,2802,"I was invited as an honorary guest"],[2802,2907,"at your graduation."],[2977,3069,"No way."],[3086,3148,"Yeah."],[3240,3332,"I did not want to miss"],[3332,3457,"the opportunity of handing you"],[3457,3536,"your diploma."],[3632,3720,"Can you please act like you"],[3720,3807,"don't know me?"],[3866,4045,"Today was embarrassing"],[4045,4112,"enough."],[4112,4200,"Oh, okay."],[4245,4346,"It's embarrassing to be seen"],[4346,4425,"dating me?"],[4629,4750,"We’re dating?"],[4808,4938,"Well, not exactly."],[4988,5067,"At the moment"],[5067,5217,"I want much more than that."]],"34":[[554,734,"It's an honor to stand in front of you today,"],[759,913,"especially as a member"],[913,1063,"of a family that's long supported"],[1063,1180,"this institution."],[1213,1522,"Oh, my God!"],[1522,1701,"He’s so hot."],[1755,1935,"Is he smiling at me?"],[2239,2469,"My family helped lay the foundation"],[2502,2635,"of this fine school."],[2635,2748,"Because we believe"],[2748,2919,"in the power of education"],[2919,3094,"to transform lives."],[3182,3290,"Congratulations."],[3549,3666,"Congratulations."],[3666,3749,"Thank you."],[4099,4283,"Congratulations, Ms. Jenkins."],[4283,4441,"Thank you, Mr. Trenton."],[4441,4583,"You should wear that gown to bed tonight."]],"35":[[20,183,"You should wear that gown to bed tonight."],[367,525,"Thank you, Mr. Trenton."],[525,617,"Nice tie."],[654,725,"Thanks."],[725,846,"Somebody very special picked it"],[846,934,"out for me this morning."],[1864,1968,"Congratulations. Thank you."],[3128,3199,"Hey, Mom."],[3257,3365,"How was Dad’s surgery?"],[3399,3520,"It went great."],[3570,3682,"Happy graduation,"],[3682,3757,"baby."],[3770,3908,"I'm sorry we couldn't be there with you."],[3908,4020,"It's okay, Mom."],[4020,4170,"I know you have to be at the hospital"],[4170,4266,"with dad right now."],[4396,4496,"I'm here with friends."],[4667,4767,"I’ll see you later."],[4825,4900,"I love you."],[5125,5338,"Maybe I should leave."],[5451,5559,"Harper Jenkins!"]],"36":[[20,104,"Happy graduation."],[308,458,"This is so sweet, Will."],[458,563,"Ms. Jenkins!"],[804,967,"Happy graduation, Ms. Jenkins."],[1222,1276,"Will?"],[1459,1539,"What are you doing here?"],[1589,1730,"You two know each other?"],[1751,1864,"This is my brother, Aaron."],[1906,2039,"I should ask you the same question."],[2039,2135,"I'm here with Harper."],[2181,2273,"What are you doing here?"],[2314,2423,"You two are brothers?"],[2460,2590,"Hold on. Uh..."],[2590,2790,"What are you doing with Harper?"],[2819,2886,"We’re..."],[3119,3190,"We're dating."],[3386,3549,"This is the girl I told you about."],[3549,3661,"You, you can't be!"],[3661,3853,"How could you be dating her? Harper?"],[3853,4016,"I know my brother. Stay away from him."],[4016,4091,"He's just going to hurt you."],[4091,4245,"Hey, watch your mouth, Aaron."],[4362,4429,"Come with me."],[4508,4621,"Don't touch her, man."],[4675,4763,"Oh my God."],[4763,4896,"The Trenton brothers are fighting over"],[4896,5009,"Harper Jenkins."],[5030,5088,"Stop it!"],[5088,5288,"What the hell is wrong with you two?"],[5492,5601,"Harper. You okay?"],[5643,5801,"I'm so sorry. I, I didn't mean..."],[6101,6177,"Harper!"],[6464,6589,"Sorry, I was..."],[6589,6677,"I was planning on giving you"],[6677,6819,"a surprise tonight."],[6819,6965,"What's going on? Are you okay?"],[7019,7169,"She's pregnant with my baby!"]],"37":[[20,79,"What's going on?"],[79,166,"Are you okay?"],[229,316,"Stop it, Will!"],[316,471,"Put me down! I can walk myself."],[471,513,"Hey!"],[583,717,"I just don't want to repeat history."],[717,842,"I wanna be extra careful with you"],[842,930,"and the baby this time."],[988,1051,"This time?"],[1121,1167,"Wow."],[1297,1405,"Less than a year since Kaitlin"],[1405,1472,"dumped you and you already"],[1472,1593,"got somebody knocked up?"],[1676,1918,"Kaitlin, the woman in the photos?"],[1918,2052,"Hey! You need to shut up."],[2081,2223,"Still can't stand to hear her name?"],[2318,2356,"Come on."],[2356,2456,"You and I both know you're not over"],[2456,2573,"your ex-fiancée."],[2652,2777,"Don't let him fool you, Harper!"],[2836,2936,"You're just his rebound."],[3073,3165,"You need to learn how to shut up"],[3165,3265,"or I'll teach you how."],[4166,4333,"Is it really like Aaron said?"],[4333,4529,"Is that why he's keeping the photo"],[4529,4604,"with Kaitlin?"],[4692,4817,"I'm sorry about Aaron."],[4900,4992,"I'll make sure he doesn't harass"],[4992,5063,"you again."],[5121,5213,"Who's Kaitlin?"]],"38":[[54,183,"Kaitlin was my fiancée."],[396,563,"She ran out on me at the altar"],[563,667,"six months ago."],[742,875,"I haven't seen her since."],[1076,1197,"I'm sorry that..."],[1197,1305,"That must have hurt."],[1409,1539,"After that, my grandfather told me"],[1539,1710,"that I need to find somebody..."],[1739,1826,"Because we need a new heir"],[1826,1897,"for the family."],[1968,2072,"But I don't want to put myself"],[2072,2147,"through that again."],[2264,2394,"That's why... That's why you"],[2469,2598,"sought out a surrogate."],[2786,2948,"You mean so much more to me now."],[2948,3044,"You know that, right?"],[3128,3169,"Yeah."],[3278,3319,"Sure."],[3428,3645,"You don't need to explain anything"],[3645,3703,"to me, Will."],[4633,4742,"You've been in this dream"],[4742,4854,"for too long, Harper."],[4867,5009,"The quicker you wake up, the better."]],"39":[[2077,2181,"Will, is"],[2181,2348,"still in touch with his ex?"],[2585,2756,"This is just a normal examination."],[2756,2869,"You can leave if you're busy."],[3065,3194,"Harper, you've been cold and distant"],[3194,3265,"to me ever since"],[3265,3365,"the graduation."],[3395,3499,"So, what's going on?"],[3616,3666,"Nothing."],[3753,3858,"I'm just trying to keep things"],[3858,3933,"clear and simple."],[3999,4087,"I'm your surrogate,"],[4087,4195,"and you are my client."],[4450,4600,"You know that's not what this is."],[4783,4842,"Harper!"],[4850,4934,"When did you become"],[4934,5021,"a surrogate?"],[5042,5105,"Mom."],[5130,5246,"That's why you haven't come to"],[5246,5401,"visit for these past few months?"],[5401,5505,"Mom, I..."],[5505,5697,"How could you have done this?"],[5730,5993,"Have I taught you nothing of shame?"],[6014,6147,"Mrs. Jenkins? Please."],[6147,6260,"We can talk about this."],[6260,6418,"Did you make my daughter do this?"],[6460,6527,"No, no."],[6527,6556,"It was..."],[6556,6685,"It was my choice. We..."],[6685,6806,"We needed the money."],[6990,7198,"You did this to pay for"],[7198,7390,"your father's medical bills?"]],"40":[[12,154,"We had no other choice."],[154,379,"Dad's surgery was too expensive."],[379,554,"There was no way we could afford it."],[692,863,"I'm fine. Mom."],[863,980,"Really."],[980,1217,"Will has been taking great care of me"],[1259,1372,"and our baby."],[1488,1584,"You’re... You're the"],[1584,1701,"biological mother?"],[1735,1889,"Yes, Mom. It's..."],[1985,2089,"It's my baby."],[2235,2427,"Oh, my poor baby."],[2552,2861,"You had an amazing future in front of you."],[2861,3015,"And now we've dragged you"],[3015,3161,"into all of this."],[3182,3332,"That's not true, Mom."],[3445,3636,"In a few months, the baby will be born"],[3636,3803,"and everything will return to normal,"],[3803,3899,"I promise."],[3941,4195,"Baby, this is your child."],[4270,4429,"Do you really think you can just"],[4429,4512,"walk away"],[4512,4696,"after you hear its first cries?"],[4838,4921,"Ms. Jenkins?"],[5021,5138,"The ultrasound is ready for you."],[5255,5321,"Go on."],[5438,5534,"We'll talk later."],[5609,5668,"Okay."]],"41":[[129,216,"There it is."],[521,633,"The baby still looks healthy."],[888,955,"Are you ready to find"],[955,1063,"out the baby's sex?"],[1101,1176,"Yes. Yes!"],[1280,1351,"Congratulations!"],[1351,1463,"You're having a baby girl!"],[1639,1739,"I'm going to be a father."],[1856,1943,"A girl."],[2268,2402,"But I can't be her mother."],[2439,2560,"I'm just a surrogate mother."],[2610,2744,"I have to leave my own baby."],[3661,3753,"How's the baby?"],[3858,4041,"Good. Mom, look."],[4079,4183,"This is your granddaughter."],[4512,4792,"Oh, she's going to be a beautiful girl."],[4896,5021,"Just like my baby girl."],[5113,5242,"I just can't believe we’re not going"],[5242,5422,"to get to see her grow up."]],"42":[[100,183,"Mrs. Jenkins."],[329,437,"Harper can stay with me as long"],[437,525,"as she pleases."],[617,750,"She's so much more than a surrogate"],[750,800,"to me."],[984,1130,"I promise, I'm going to take"],[1130,1197,"good care of her."],[1368,1443,"That's right, Mom."],[1576,1643,"I trust him."],[1739,1780,"Alright,"],[1914,2139,"I'll trust you this time."],[2298,2464,"And you better take good care of"],[2464,2544,"of my daughter"],[2694,2811,"and my granddaughter."],[3249,3307,"Will"],[3307,3395,"Trenton."],[3474,3595,"So this is why you haven't been"],[3595,3770,"returning my calls?"],[3812,3991,"Because you found a surrogate"],[3991,4099,"to replace me?"],[4312,4491,"You're my fiancé."],[4579,4700,"What happened to forever?"]],"43":[[1418,1476,"Will, I..."],[1476,1630,"I think we need to sleep"],[1630,1797,"in separate rooms from now on."],[1885,2027,"We should have done that months ago."],[2085,2181,"Is this because of what your mother"],[2181,2306,"said today at the hospital?"],[2344,2585,"Harper, I want you here with me."],[2619,2681,"No, it's..."],[2819,2952,"It's not because of her."],[2952,3069,"It's because of..."],[3165,3278,"It's because of you."]],"44":[[37,225,"It's because of us."],[241,300,"Harper."],[387,513,"I know you said those things"],[513,646,"back there to..."],[646,792,"to calm my mother down. I..."],[855,938,"I get that."],[1163,1201,"I..."],[1384,1639,"I’m trying so hard to not"],[1639,1835,"get the wrong idea and"],[1856,2052,"and distance myself from..."],[2052,2206,"from you, from..."],[2289,2423,"from the baby."],[2677,2706,"But the"],[2706,2982,"situation makes it impossible."],[3048,3290,"Like, what if I just start falling"],[3290,3411,"in love with you?"],[3561,3778,"I think I just need to distance myself"],[3778,4049,"from you and stick to the contract. And..."],[4817,4938,"Fuck the contract."],[5105,5242,"Stay and raise our daughter with me."],[5309,5467,"But... But, what are you saying?"],[5467,5601,"I'm saying, saying you should stay here."],[5672,5839,"You should be my girlfriend, Harper."],[5893,6026,"Let’s start a family together."]],"45":[[79,129,"Look,"],[204,412,"I need you to raise this baby with me."],[462,604,"I can't do this without you."],[2548,2694,"J&T's baby girl."],[2694,2877,"Jenkins and Trenton's baby girl."],[2982,3119,"I had that specially made."],[3445,3570,"Look, I've been thinking about this"],[3570,3666,"for a while now."],[3728,3824,"Let's raise her together."],[3895,4041,"Be the parents that she needs."],[4266,4362,"I, uh..."],[4362,4429,"Harper,"],[4542,4625,"please say yes."],[4783,4850,"Please."],[5134,5380,"Yes, I’d love to."],[5968,6051,"I'll introduce you"],[6051,6193,"to everybody at my grandfather's"],[6193,6239,"birthday."],[6356,6468,"They're gonna love you."],[6502,6606,"They're gonna love you."]],"46":[[533,709,"What is this?"],[734,888,"Well, the doctor said to start using"],[888,1071,"massage oil to prevent"],[1071,1301,"stretch marks on your thighs"],[1301,1422,"on your belly, on your chest."],[1422,1697,"So, I thought that I'd help you with that."],[1710,1835,"You want to do that?"],[1881,1935,"Yeah."],[2018,2185,"It's a father's job, right?"],[3040,3103,"Okay."],[4537,4642,"He's so sweet."],[4771,4879,"Now it's time for the chest."],[4921,4992,"My chest?"],[4996,5059,"Yeah."],[5088,5163,"No way."]],"47":[[41,91,"Come on."],[212,387,"The doctor recommended it, so."],[729,792,"Oops!"],[809,980,"Now Daddy's covered with oil, too."],[2460,2565,"Will Trenton's here."],[2615,2686,"Who's the lady"],[2686,2752,"he's with?"],[2994,3107,"She's pregnant?"],[3174,3307,"And with Will's baby?"],[3307,3490,"But I thought he was still hung up"],[3490,3632,"on his ex-fiancée?"],[3699,3824,"They're staring at me."],[3862,3995,"Don't worry about them."],[4254,4316,"I'm here."],[4850,4988,"Oh, there he is."],[4988,5117,"Happy birthday, Grandpa."],[5276,5530,"This is my girlfriend, Harper Jenkins."],[5551,5747,"This is my mom, Jessica, and"],[5876,6022,"my brother, Aaron."]],"48":[[258,425,"Happy birthday, Mr. Trenton."],[513,713,"You have a lovely house,"],[713,817,"Mrs. Trenton."],[1163,1334,"I've heard so much about you,"],[1334,1426,"Ms. Jenkins."],[1497,1730,"I don't know why my grandson"],[1760,1964,"took so long to introduce you."],[2031,2127,"I don't bite."],[2210,2285,"It was me."],[2339,2485,"I heard so many wonderful things"],[2485,2660,"about you, Mr. Trenton."],[2665,2740,"I was just"],[2794,2882,"nervous."],[2982,3169,"Will, why did you keep"],[3169,3315,"her hidden so long?"],[3370,3478,"It’s so unlike you."],[3599,3732,"What's really going on?"]],"49":[[62,112,"Be nice,"],[112,171,"Jessica."],[379,513,"She has a good reason"],[513,613,"to be nervous."],[713,821,"We're all crazy here."],[980,1272,"So I heard from a little birdie that,"],[1330,1409,"she's a girl."],[1630,1685,"Come on."],[2456,2577,"Thank you, everyone,"],[2577,2811,"for coming and helping me"],[2811,2948,"celebrate my birthday."],[3019,3098,"And now"],[3269,3370,"I have a big announcement"],[3370,3516,"to make today."],[3516,3812,"I made up my mind long ago"],[3933,4145,"to leave my entire estate"],[4241,4558,"to my first born great grandchild."],[4721,4833,"And that’s..."],[4833,5005,"That's my son."],[5355,5438,"Kaitlin?"],[5555,5622,"Kaitlin?"],[5634,5797,"Will's ex-fiancée?"],[5868,6064,"You left my son at the altar."],[6064,6214,"How dare you show up in this"],[6214,6314,"house again?"],[6360,6514,"I'm the one that's pregnant"],[6514,6648,"with Will's firstborn."],[6656,6840,"My son is the rightful heir to the"],[6840,6931,"Trenton family."]],"50":[[150,216,"Hi, Will."],[400,525,"I missed you."],[550,688,"It's good to see you again."],[754,959,"Are you happy to see me and our baby?"],[1109,1180,"What’s..."],[1180,1280,"What's going on, Will?"],[1280,1526,"No, Harper, I promise."],[1526,1680,"I did not get her pregnant."],[1710,1910,"I know you're still mad at me"],[1910,2027,"for leaving our wedding,"],[2027,2260,"but you can't disown your own child."],[2331,2473,"I found out as soon as I left,"],[2473,2627,"and then I didn't know what to do,"],[2627,2765,"I panicked."],[2765,2902,"I didn't know how to tell you."],[3032,3174,"You have to trust me."],[3203,3340,"This is your baby."],[3428,3603,"Here, feel."],[3674,3812,"That’s our son."],[3841,3928,"I don't believe a word coming out"],[3928,4008,"of your mouth."],[4008,4137,"Harper."],[4137,4295,"This isn't my child."],[4295,4487,"My only child is with my girlfriend"],[4487,4592,"Harper!"],[4592,4704,"Your girlfriend?"],[4783,4875,"How long are you going to"],[4875,5025,"keep your family in the dark?"],[5046,5163,"She's only a surrogate"],[5163,5226,"you hired."],[5488,5684,"What's she talking about, Will?"]],"51":[[0,137,"She’s only a surrogate?"],[137,250,"What a scandal!"],[329,404,"Oh, my."],[425,546,"Is this true?"],[613,863,"Is she just a surrogate you hired?"],[905,955,"Will!"],[1030,1096,"Explain."],[1096,1188,"No. She..."],[1359,1447,"She was."],[1447,1651,"Look, that's in the past, okay?"],[1651,1730,"We're dating now."],[1881,1964,"Harper's my girlfriend,"],[2056,2202,"and we're raising this child together."],[2235,2398,"Will, how can you lie"],[2398,2681,"and bring some random woman"],[2681,2823,"into our family?"],[2831,3028,"How dare you hire a surrogate"],[3057,3244,"to carry my great grandchild!"],[3307,3445,"A bottom feeder!"],[3465,3649,"Who's selling her own womb?"],[3649,3774,"Mr. Trenton, I..."],[3853,3987,"Grandpa, stop it!"],[4045,4225,"She's not like that. You understand me?"],[4250,4391,"The baby will live with us"],[4391,4512,"after she's born."],[4567,4642,"But you!"],[4804,4925,"You'll never be accepted"],[4925,5013,"by our family."]],"52":[[12,79,"Grandpa."],[208,275,"Mom."],[396,479,"It's not your call"],[479,571,"whether she stays or not."],[571,679,"She's part of my life."],[775,829,"And there's nothing"],[829,900,"that you can say"],[900,988,"that will ever change that."],[1163,1368,"How dare you side with the surrogate"],[1368,1522,"over your own family?"],[1605,1893,"I can't do without her in my life"],[1985,2089,"because I love her."],[2218,2385,"He loves me?"],[2423,2481,"Fuck!"],[2481,2648,"How could Will already fall in love"],[2648,2740,"with this slut?"],[2740,2915,"Are you insane?"],[2915,3103,"Do you hear what you're saying?"],[3103,3261,"I love her so much."],[3403,3582,"Actually, I want her to be more than just"],[3582,3674,"my girlfriend."],[3991,4291,"He can't seriously be planning to propose."],[4300,4433,"I have to stop him."],[4633,4775,"Ahh!"],[4800,5025,"Ow! Ahh! My stomach!"],[5100,5184,"It hurts!"]],"53":[[8,120,"My stomach!"],[166,254,"It hurts!"],[333,429,"Oh no!"],[592,867,"Will... Take her to the hospital now!"],[925,1071,"Please,